Danila goes to his older brother to start a new life in Petersburg. His brother is a gangster and a killer, and he puts Danila into this criminal world asking him to kill someone. There his new life starts, he meets new people, a girl, becomes a big fan of the rock band &quot;Nautilus Pompillius&quot;. Now he is a killer, and killing is easier than living for him. Realizing this makes him understand he is going the wrong way.


